  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dashpong is a unique and fast-paced local multiplayer game. High energy and sometimes chaotic, it's the perfect arcade game to play with your friends!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You move freely on the map and create physics based paddles when dashing. Push the ball into your opponents' goal by throwing your paddles across the map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game is multiplayer only, there's no single player experience yet.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create paddles at the last moment to protect your goal!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/0a259da360cc7eb62739ff3c45a821e0.poster.avif?t=1771448094\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/0a259da360cc7eb62739ff3c45a821e0.webm?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/0a259da360cc7eb62739ff3c45a821e0.mp4?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use the environment to your advantage!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/8374a8789665c1ef28dd5b90c96edf81.poster.avif?t=1771448094\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/8374a8789665c1ef28dd5b90c96edf81.webm?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/8374a8789665c1ef28dd5b90c96edf81.mp4?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dashing to create paddle can save you, but be careful, it can be turned against you! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/d5e7b592ce41f5ede26653d6166b3e54.poster.avif?t=1771448094\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/d5e7b592ce41f5ede26653d6166b3e54.webm?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/d5e7b592ce41f5ede26653d6166b3e54.mp4?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UP TO 4 PLAYERS: More people, more chaos, more fun! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/e1f59a0f54555a950ea53f8d20ce1fca.poster.avif?t=1771448094\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/e1f59a0f54555a950ea53f8d20ce1fca.webm?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/e1f59a0f54555a950ea53f8d20ce1fca.mp4?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Small goals, weird angles, obstacles, all kinds of maps! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/0808d466ae09e5540a2bf5121e8d1208.poster.avif?t=1771448094\" width=1170 height=588 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/0808d466ae09e5540a2bf5121e8d1208.webm?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/0808d466ae09e5540a2bf5121e8d1208.mp4?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MANY SPECIAL MODES: Rewind, portals, gravity wells, invisible paddles, and many, many more! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/b7a8d9526c099c04678535dc14b813a3.poster.avif?t=1771448094\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/b7a8d9526c099c04678535dc14b813a3.webm?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/b7a8d9526c099c04678535dc14b813a3.mp4?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your team colors!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/21e2d28041addfe6a943e2fbbc0dddfb.poster.avif?t=1771448094\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/21e2d28041addfe6a943e2fbbc0dddfb.webm?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/21e2d28041addfe6a943e2fbbc0dddfb.mp4?t=1771448094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729250/extras/2ffff2fbaaa3f01221abcd9d4912760c.avif?t=1771448094\" width=601 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the <strong>classic mode</strong>, with just you and the paddles or the <strong>arcade mode</strong> with tons of special modes bending the rules to renew your experience and challenge your skills: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10+ maps</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1V1, 2V2</strong> or <strong>3V1</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>25+ Special modes</strong> with power ups, crazy environments and twisted rules: multiple balls, changing gravity, time rewind, destructible environment, power ups, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team color</strong> selection: choose the color that suits your team the best</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom </strong>mode: You control everything: maps, player size, strength, number of paddles and balls, etc.. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here is a list of the accessibility features in Dashpong</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tunable player's color</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Localized in different languages (see languages on Steam)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tunable controller vibration</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tunable screenshake</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the custom mode, you can change many parameters:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player size</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player speed</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paddle number</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dash duration</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hit strength</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ball size</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ball number</strong></p></li></ul>",
